hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實也很正常<br />\n不過有人賣就同時有人接<br />\n<br />\n賣的基楚投資者（VC）是這樣運作的<br />\n它們錢多，不斷找有潛力的初創公司來投<br />\n分幾10注分散投幾10間（可以更多），只要有一間成長到，就可帶來20-100倍回報。<br />\n<br />\n一間賺，足以賺返其餘90%蝕的<br />\n當一間能夠成長，培育呢一間再成長，回報就會比再找新公司回報來得高。<br />\n<br />\n又要成長，又要繼續找新公司怎辦？<br />\n就是ipo後有脫手機會，走一半（或一大部分），拎返成本（及利潤），再找其他新公司，留下的又可以保持再增長"},{"pid":"fb70540823e1b8061b8ebad450e5b6a51e6671fb","tid":306992,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T07:11:16.000Z","msg":"17蚊插一半真係有機會做第二隻700<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"1e5306a56b1dd497f730d46e2f995003600cbbae","tid":306992,"uid":8113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T07:23:19.000Z","msg":"大量沽緊小心睇路"},{"pid":"09bf62c3b8528f1c6899c3433d92d058f9fa7c0e","tid":306992,"uid":96757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:21:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多股東抛售喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會升?"},{"pid":"4fe30b493207927129237ba2d1cd96d1a3380ed4","tid":306992,"uid":113125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T09:31:17.000Z","msg":"有緣看到的人<br />\n有福了"},{"pid":"93ec60c245377f48f24e2bab5a6e66f40e915d84","tid":306992,"uid":5278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T09:46:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有緣看到的人<br />\n有福了</blockquote><br />\n本身都留意緊<br />\n但你成個錢主席咁款<br />\n不了"},{"pid":"3219bd03ac6ea865228ae26b45ee7df6ca39ee07","tid":306992,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T11:31:37.000Z","msg":"第二隻amzn<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"525135d094c57b9331d37e8dc3b05f40016467f6","tid":306992,"uid":29008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T00:59:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class